主要翻译
 
mobilize [sb/sth] # vtr (make ready for action)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 动员 dòng yuán  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 调动 dòng yuán，diào dòng TC Traditional Chinese 調動 
 -- Successful candidates must mobilize minority voters.
 -- 成功的竞选人必须动员少数选民。
 
mobilize, also UK: mobilise vi (prepare for action)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 准备行动 zhǔn bèi xíng dòng TC Traditional Chinese 準備行動  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 机动化 zhǔn bèi xíng dòng，jī dòng huà TC Traditional Chinese 機動化 
 -- Troops have been mobilizing on both sides of the border.
 -- 军队一直在边境两边准备行动。

在这些条目还发现' mobilize '：
中文：
调动

标题中含有单词 'mobilize' 的论坛讨论：



mobilize into

Mobilize someone on the rights

Mobilize the new economy through

mobilize to

procedures and routines were established to mobilize this talent on a regular basis...

